Advanced techniques for better performance.

**1. Compressed Trie (Radix Tree)**
Merge single-child chains into one edge.
```
Before:         After:
  a               abc
  |                |
  b               xyz
  |               
  c              
  |
  ...
```

**2. Ternary Search Tree**
Each node has 3 children: less, equal, greater.
Better memory than 26-way Trie.

**3. Word Storage at Nodes**
